{"tid":1970511,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】李嘉誠拍片感謝醫護　「香港醫護，好嘢」","createTime":"2020-04-13T08:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T23:53:03.000Z","uid":30788,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3116cb80042fb2fb2b72fc02ad40a414cd887a5f","tid":1970511,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，醫護人員工作壓力急增，李嘉誠基金會今日（13 日）在 FB 發布影片，基金會主席、長和系資深顧問李嘉誠，在影片中感謝醫護人員的辛勞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">片段僅長約 4 秒</span></span>，李嘉誠坐在一張木椅上，向鏡頭打「讚好」手勢，「香港醫護，好嘢。」影片繼而出現「Thank U，謝謝你哋」的字樣。基金會在影片下方寫到﹐「在陽光絢麗的一天，李先生由衷地多謝香港醫護每一位」，且附上「#香港醫護了不起」、「#抗疫英雄」的標籤。"},{"pid":"0048a2a6d0b30133774bf6064538e6ced10fd82a","tid":1970511,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7-%E5%A5%BD%E5%98%A2/?fbclid=IwAR0MG1Svy3GapE9V75xUrZqyAAJ04GdQuPozLDI7qFpqU5jZA-8eyk_MnlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%2598%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0MG1Svy3GapE9V75xUrZqyAAJ04GdQuPozLDI7qFpqU5jZA-8eyk_MnlQ&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=d0f2c62d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD